			"description": "This module requires students to conduct an independent research project on an approved topic under the supervision of an academic staff. The research project, which usually includes some fieldwork, will be submitted as an Honours Thesis.",
			"prerequisite": "Cohort 2006 and before: (1) Complete at least 100MCs including 56MCs of SC major requirement and (2) Obtain one of the following minimum standards at the point of registration: (a) minimum CAP of 4.0 or (b) minimum SJAP of 4.0 and CAP of 3.5. Cohort 2007 onwards: Completed 110MCs including 60MCs of SC major requirements with a minimum SJAP of 4.0 and CAP of 3.5.",
